{"tid":2351339,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港人移台數字料破萬 台擬再放寛移民限制","createTime":"2021-01-03T06:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T07:28:36.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e7945129be3ef4e96c3ff5ad9ec4a818e5d095ec","tid":2351339,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:39:18.000Z","msg":"根據台灣移民署最新統計，截至2020年11月底，獲許可在台居留的香港居民人數高達9,501人，已超過去年全年5,858人，預估2020底可突破1萬大關。<br />\n<br />\n統計資料顯示，今年前11個月，港人來台居留許可9,501人、定居許可人數1,397人，只計11月居留許可已有2,027人，創下今年以來單月新高紀錄，越來越多香港人選擇移居台灣。<br />\n<br />\n台灣的國家發展委員會（國發會）日前完成《外國專業人才延攬及僱用法》修訂草案法規預告程序，新規定放寬港澳居民在台創業移民的限制，只要在指定集資平台投資200萬元新台幣（約56萬港幣），就可以向台灣有關部門申請創業家簽證，條訂草案近日將報請台灣行政院審議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210103/DTKNPY42WBFXVPMZEPVNH4KYLM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210103%2FDTKNPY42WBFXVPMZEPVNH4KYLM%2F&d=r3XH83vhlb%2FNbb5A40Y%2F0LidffPqrKRYdMEHu3E%2BQw4%3D&h=5b62fcd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210103%2FDTKNPY42WBFXVPMZEPVNH4KYLM%2F&h=1a7616d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210103/DTKNPY42WBFXVPMZEPVNH4KYLM/</a>"},{"pid":"2f8e6005498f67aeca336764445d46ea815e784f","tid":2351339,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"182ab23d07e85bffa3a227876490e020894aacbc","tid":2351339,"uid":384590,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:41:32.000Z","msg":"預計到依個post既reply<br />\n五毛 分化撚！<br />\n拉！"},{"pid":"f7666770c4c7835500ce244c7eac80e73e9e8ed6","tid":2351339,"uid":242537,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"182ab23d07e85bffa3a227876490e020894aacbc","tid":2351339,"uid":384590,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T06:41:32.000Z","msg":"預計到依個post既reply<br />\n五毛 分化撚！<br />\n拉